'''維羅·查爾斯·德里菲爾德'''（{{lang|en|Vero Charles Driffield}}，{{bd|1858年|5月7日|1915年|11月14日}}）是[[英國|英國]][[化學家|化學家]]，他潛心研究[[攝影|攝影]][[膠卷|膠卷]]{{tsl|en|Sensitometry|感光測定}}及[[密度測定法|密度測定]]之關係，與[[菲迪南·赫爾特|菲迪南·赫爾特]]一同提出[[HD曲線|HD曲線]]，合作發表八篇論文。1898年，他們榮獲{{tsl|en|Royal Photographic Society|皇家攝影學會}}的進步奬。<ref>Hardie, pp173–174</ref><ref name="RPS_2011_Progress_Medal_1898">Royal Photographic Society. ''Progress medal''. Web-page listing people, who have received this award since 1878 ({{cite web|url=http://www.rps.org/annual-awards/Progress-medal |title=Archived copy |accessdate=19 April 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120822030453/http://www.rps.org/annual-awards/Progress-Medal |archivedate=22 August 2012 }}): "Instituted in 1878, this medal is awarded in recognition of any invention, research, publication or other contribution which has resulted in an important advance in the scientific or technological development of photography or imaging in the widest sense. This award also carries with it an Honorary Fellowship of The Society. […] 1898 [[Ferdinand_Hurter|Ferdinand Hurter]] and Vero C Driffield […]"</ref>

